Skill: Ainspect    Timer: None         GL:  7    Cost: 20
This is the Fighter's ability to take his/her knowledge of armor and inspect
a piece of armor to learn the details of it.

This allows the Fighter to judge the quality of the armor on many fronts.

It is said that some armor is well known throughout the lands, and often
Fighters remember from whence it came.


Syntax is: ainspect <armor>
